In re Resignation of Kohnen.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Kohnen (1995), 72 Ohio St.3d 1216.]

(No. 95-1109 Submitted June 21, 1995 Decided June 22, 1995.)

The resignation as an attorney of David A. Kohnen of Cincinnati, Ohio, Attorney Registration No. 0006638, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., concur.
